# SwiftRide â€“ Non-Negotiables

1. No simulated transactions
2. No fake balances
3. Every transaction must:
   - Have a Transaction ID
   - Have a Status
   - Be traceable to a user
4. WhatsApp is the primary interface
5. Google Sheets is the live ledger until replaced
6. Manual override is allowed but logged
7. No silent failures
8. Every error must be visible
9. Every action must leave an audit trail
10. System must work on a phone

